responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F05C76C94C3442F2D20FC296852C8D26", "You know, Nil Feann\'s death spooked a lot of the good folk. But who\'s got time to mourn? I certainly don\'t. All the grief\'s been stonewalled for the festive atmosphere. And we could use some good ol\' fashioned merrymaking. The only killjoy around here is Eliza, but she\'s not gloomy about the nobles. She\'s been pining for a missing fellow. I keep reassuring her that he probably just had a few too many drinks and lost his way home, but it\'s no use. She\'s convinced he\'s in some sort of trouble.")
name: MADD_0009_Cowering_BartenderJames_18
